song.title: Infravaganza Galore
song.info:
Soundtrack for the demo Twogather by 3LN shown at both Outline 2012 and MAiN Splash 2012.
The demo can be seen live on 3LN's website : [url]http://3ln.eu/twogather/[/url]
The soundtrack (ogg) can be downloaded from Den's Soundcloud: [url]https://soundcloud.com/den/infravaganza-galore-twogather[/url]
